{
  "texts": [
    "We also perform an in-depth comparison and analysis of the experimental parameters.",
    "Finally, to illustrate a practical application of the proposed method, we provide a case study on a real dataset (Sect. 5).",
    "Related WorkWith the initial introduction of community search [17], there has been a proliferation of variants in recent years.",
    "These variants are applied to homogeneous graphs, attribute graphs, heterogeneous graphs, and dynamic graphs, but their core focus remains on discovering tightly connected communities that satisfy specific constraints.",
    "Community detection and community search represent two main categories of studies related to finding communities on graphs [18][19][20].Community detection algorithms have been studied extensively on both homogeneous and heterogeneous graphs [21][22][23][24]."
  ]
}